data.description:
Updated 2 story home in neighborhood with mature landscaping; 4 Bedrooms, all upstairs; 2.5 Bathrooms; downstairs office; 3 living areas; Dining; Kitchen w/granite, stainless appliances, and eat in breakfast area; HUGE master bedroom; Master bath with walk in shower and separate jetted tub; Stained concrete floors down; updated appliances; 2 Car attached garage; remote gate on driveway and much more. 

Fantastic Tomball schools. Lakewood Elementary, Northpointe Intermediate, Willowood Jr. High, Tomball Memorial HS.
